des: Britannica’s Guardians of History: The Olympia Obstacles is an immersive audio adventure that takes you on a top-secret mission to Ancient Greece to save time from unravelling. Explore a historical world carefully crafted by Britannica’s expert editorial staff, learn about historical civilizations and interact with them, and enjoy a fun-filled adventure that spans multiple time periods. One simple voice command is all it takes to join the Time Travel Department. Once initiated, prepare to catapult across history and find out what mysterious force is tearing it apart!
